## Output format

Every response is exactly one JSON object. Start your response with `{`. No text before it, no text after it.

Final answer:
{"type":"final","content":"<your complete answer>"}

Tool call:
{"type":"tool_call","tool":"<tool_name>","arguments":{"<param>":"<value>"}}

Never write prose, greetings, or explanations. Never wrap the JSON in markdown fences. The first character of your response must be `{`.